data-weight="0.5" ><div id="panel-w5d0cf912abc42-1-1-0" class="so-panel widget widget_black-studio-tinymce widget_black_studio_tinymce panel-first-child panel-last-child" data-index="2" data-style="{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;}" ><div class="textwidget"><span class="fontstyle0">1. Package stand</span><span class="fontstyle2">: 2,700USD/ 9sq.m\nstand\n• Carpeted (3m x 3m)\n• 03 partitions\n• Fascia with company name\n• 01 in formation counter\n• 02 chairs\n• 01 waste paper basket\n• 02 fluorescent tubes\n• 01 electric socket of 05 Amp/220V\n2. </span><span class="fontstyle0">Space only\n</span><span class="fontstyle2">• Indoor raw space: USD 285/sq.m\n</span><span class="fontstyle3">Exhibitors will build their own stands\nElectricity and carpet are not available</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div>', 'Product Zone', 'Vietnam Expo 2019 will take place from April 10-13, 2019 at the 91 Tran Hung Dao Exhibition Center, Hoan Kiem, Hanoi, displaying and introducing many new technology products.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '130-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-06-21 22:34:42', '2019-06-21 15:34:42', '', 130, 'http://elevator_vnexpo.co/130-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
