 nền kinh tế Việt Nam và Liên bang Nga. Thống kê từ Ban tổ chức, đã có khoảng 8.000 lượt khách là các tập đoàn kinh tế Việt Nam, các doanh nghiệp, cá nhân tới tham gia các hoạt động xúc tiến thương mại tại khu gian hàng quốc gia Nga.\r\n<table class="__MB_template_g">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="__RE_PLACE_CONTENT">Vietnam Expo 2019 do Bộ Công Thương chủ trì, Cục Xúc tiến thương mại chỉ đạo và Công ty Vinexad tổ chức, sẽ mở cửa từ 9h sáng đến 18h chiều các ngày 10-13/4/2019 tại Trung tâm Triển lãm quốc tế – 91 Trần Hưng Đạo, Hoàn Kiếm, Hà Nội.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>', '550 doanh nghiệp sẽ tham dự VIETNAM EXPO 2019', 'Vietnam Expo 2019 do Bộ Công Thương chủ trì, Cục Xúc tiến thương mại chỉ đạo và Công ty Vinexad tổ chức, sẽ mở cửa từ 9h sáng đến 18h chiều các ngày 10-13/4/2019 tại Trung tâm Triển lãm quốc tế – 91 Trần Hưng Đạo, Hoàn Kiếm, Hà Nội.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '193-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-06-22 21:56:00', '2019-06-22 14:56:00', '', 193, 'http://elevator_vnexpo.co/193-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(196, 1, '2019-06-22 21:56:00', '2019-06-22 14:56:00', '<div class="article-desc fw lt clearfix"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">In 2019, the International Trade Fair (Vietnam Expo) - Vietnam''s oldest and most prestigious trade promotion event will continue to be organized in scale, promoting the role of a trade promotion event. import and export and investment, bringing Vietnamese products to the world.</span></span></div>\r\n<div class="__MASTERCMS_CONTENT_BODY clearfix">\r\n\r\n<strong><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">Diversified commodity model</span></span></strong>\r\n\r\n<span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">Vietnam Expo is a key event chaired by the Ministry of Industry and Trade (Trade Promotion Agency), receiving strong support from local ministries, branches, domestic and foreign promotion organizations. </span><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">In 2019, this event will be held in 4 days, from April 10-13, 2019 at the International Exhibition Center (ICE) - 91 Tran Hung Dao, Hanoi. </span><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">Since then, continue to build a diversified and unique business model, linking trade and commerce to help domestic and foreign enterprises achieve high efficiency, contributing positively to Vietnam to strengthen regional economic integration. regional and international</span></span>\r\n\r\n<span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">Information from the organizer and fair this year will have the participation of 550 enterprises from 20 countries and territories such as Algeria, India, Cambodia, Canada, Armenia, Russia, Cuba, Taiwan, Korea. China, Laos, Malaysia, Myanmar, Nepal, Japan, China; </span><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">along with over 15,000 trade visitors to visit and work.</span></span>\r\n\r\n<span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">According to the Organizing Committee, due to limited infrastructure, the Organizing Committee selected typical businesses to attend in accordance with the stalls: International Area - Vietnam National Brand Area (Vietnam Value) - Zone of industrial products, consumer food. </span><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">At this time, the organizers and the participating businesses are actively preparing to bring to Vietnam Expo 2019 the latest products and technologies in the impressive and elaborate investment-designed booths.</span></span>\r\n\r\n<span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">In addition to an eye-catching and attractive international area, visitors will be attracted by advanced and diversified products, the presence of national brand enterprises, notably the products associated with the values. Core: "Quality - Innovation - Innovation - Pioneering capacity". </span><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">At Vietnam Expo, international partners can meet pioneering exporters in many product groups such as plastic, rubber, paper, construction materials, industrial auxiliary ...</span></span>\r\n\r\n<span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">The parallel goal of businesses is to promote and enhance the value of Vietnamese brands to develop the domestic market. </span><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">Mr. Nguyen Van Ly - representative of Viglacera said that seeing the efficiency after each fair participation is very clear, businesses have a large number of customers, especially international visitors who are interested in new products that are weak. environmentally friendly element. </span><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">Therefore, businesses are looking forward to continuing to participate in upcoming trade events.</span></span>\r\n\r\n<span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">More than just attending a fair to find new supplies, at the Vietnam Expo 2019, visitors will receive the necessary advice on design, market research, idea development. brand and product packaging through the product design and development support zone, organized by the Korea Design Promotion Institute (KIDP) and Vietnam Trade Promotion Department.</span></span>\r\n\r\n<span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">Besides, according to the Fair Organizing Committee, with the orientation to increase attraction of foreign investment, at Vietnam Expo, the Vietnam Investment and Industrial Development Promotion Zone (Invest in Vietnam) will continue to be The highlight is not only a beautiful booth design, providing updated information about the investment environment in Vietnam but also introducing international investors to 6 key industries attracting the attraction associated with investment destinations are typical localities.</span></span>\r\n\r\n<strong><span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">Enhancing regional and international economic connectivity</span></span></strong>\r\n\r\n<span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">Vietnam Expo is not only a first-ever trade promotion event of Vietnam held annually for nearly three decades but also an event of resonance due to the diversity of products and products. Quality - Prestigious - creative brand of Vietnam introduces to international friends.</span></span>\r\n\r\n<span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">In 2018, Vietnam Expo gathered 500 businesses from 23 countries and territories, including 6 international pavilions from Russia, Cuba, Korea, Nepal, China and Vietnam. </span><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">A special feature of Vietnam Expo is that the products are diversified and unique, which are specialized display in each area including: International pavilion zone, National brand area (Vietnam Value), machinery and equipment area, Food and drink area.</span></span>\r\n\r\n<span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">Judging by Vietnam Expo, Ms. Nguyen Thi Oanh - General Director of Hoang Minh Joint Stock Company - said that the quality of enterprises participating in the fair is very potential. </span><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">Determining the source of such customers, when participating in the trade fair, always bring products that fully meet the standards to supply for large corporations and enterprises.</span></span>\r\n\r\n<span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">In addition, Mr. Nguyen Van Ly - Viglacera representative said that, through Vietnam Expo, enterprises have the opportunity to further strengthen relationships with partners to enhance the brand''s position and promote export. Exporting new products to markets in and outside the region.</span></span>\r\n\r\n<span style="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">Not only is it effective for local businesses, but many countries'' pavilions have made positive judgments for Vietnam Expo. </span><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">For example, in 2018, the exhibition area of ​​the Russian Federation - the guest of Vietnam Expo is especially attracted by the elite products of Russian industry such as: precision engineering, automation, weapons and processing. creating aircraft, high-tech electronics ... According to representatives of the Russian Federation pavilion, high-level meetings, seminars taking place during the fair days help open promising cooperation between the two platforms. Vietnam''s economy and the Russian Federation. </span><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">Statistics from the Organizing Committee, there are about 8,000 visitors are Vietnamese economic groups, businesses,</span></span>\r\n<table class="__MB_template_g">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="__RE_PLACE_CONTENT"><spa