(202, 1, '2019-06-22 21:58:54', '2019-06-22 14:58:54', '<strong>Vietnam Expo 2019 will be held from April 10-13, 2019 at ICE International Exhibition Center – 91 Tran Hung Dao, Hoan Kiem, Hanoi. Representatives of the Organizing Committee said they would select typical businesses to attend in accordance with the booths: International Area – Vietnam National Brand Area (Vietnam Value) – Industrial Products Zone – Real Zone Consumer products. Especially, at Vietnam Expo this year, there will be the latest products and technologies in the impressive and elaborately designed pavilions.</strong>\r\n<div>\r\n\r\nWith the history of a prestigious and long-term trade promotion event in Vietnam, Vietnam Expo has always affirmed that through every year of organization and in 2019 – after a year of prosperity of the Vietnamese economy. , import and export turnover and investment all achieved encouraging signs of growth. Vietnam Expo continues to promote the role of an event to promote import and export trade and investment, bringing Vietnamese products to the world and vice versa.\r\n\r\n” <em>Quality – Innovation – Innovation – Pioneering capacity</em>“Are the core values ​​that products, equipment and technology are exhibited at the exhibition. In addition to the International Zone, it is eye-catching and attractive to visitors because of its advanced and diversified products, the presence of the National Brand Enterprises (VIETNAM VALUE) is a high-performance product. , expressing the intelligence and creative ability of Vietnamese people are also meticulously and professionally introduced. At Vietnam Expo, international partners can meet pioneering exporters in many product groups such as plastic, rubber, paper, construction materials, industrial aids, … Parallel objectives of enterprises are promoting and enhancing Vietnamese brand value to develop the domestic market.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<figure><img class="wp-image-151 size-full aligncenter" src="http://vietnamexpo.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/1.1.jpg" alt="" width="460" height="306" /></figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>Until this time Algeria, India, Cambodia, Canada, CH Armenia, Federal Republic of Russia, Cuba, Taiwan, South Korea, Laos, Malaysia, Myanmar, Nepal, Japan, China were countries and territories. Officially present at Vietnam Expo, this year’s Fair is expected to attract attendees from 20 countries and territories, along with over 15,000 trade visitors to visit and work during the time. Fair 4 days.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<figure><img class="aligncenter wp-image-152 size-full" src="http://vietnamexpo.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/1.2.jpg" alt="" width="460" height="307" /></figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>\r\n\r\nEvaluating the effectiveness of participating in the exhibition, Mr. Nguyen Van Ly – Viglacera representative said that “ <em>we realize that after each fair participation, we have a large and special customer base. is an international customer who is interested in new products with environmental friendly elements such as V-Smart smart hygiene, White-bone Granite tiles, energy-saving glass, baked clay bricks … Through Vietnam Expo, we He hoped to further strengthen the relationship with partners to enhance the position of Viglacera brand, promote the export of new products to markets in and outside the region</em> ”.\r\n\r\nVietnam Expo 2019 is chaired by the Ministry of Industry and Trade, directed by the Vietnam Trade Promotion Agency and organized by VINEXAD, which will be open from 9:00 to 18:00 on 10-13 April 2019 at the 91 Tran Hung Dao Exhibition Center Hoan Kiem, Hanoi.\r\n\r\n</div>', 'Many latest technology products will be displayed in VIETNAM EXPO 2019', 'Vietnam Expo 2019 will be held from April 10-13, 2019 at ICE International Exhibition Center – 91 Tran Hung Dao, Hoan Kiem, Hanoi. Representatives of the Organizing Committee said they would select typical businesses to attend in accordance with the booths: International Area – Vietnam National Brand Area (Vietnam Value) – Industrial Products Zone – Real Zone Consumer products. Especially, at Vietnam Expo this year, there will be the latest products and technologies in the impressive and elaborately designed pavilions.', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'many-latest-technology-products-will-be-displayed-in-vietnam-expo-2019', '', '', '2019-06-22 22:04:43', '2019-06-22 15:04:43', '', 0, 'http://elevator_vnexpo.co/?p=202', 0, 'post', '', 0),
