le="vertical-align: inherit;"><span style="vertical-align: inherit;">Vietnam Expo 2019 is expected to have the participation of 550 businesses and welcome about 15.00 domestic and foreign visitors to trade in 4 days, from April 10-13, 2019 at 91 Tran Hung Dao Exhibition Center , Hoan Kiem, Hanoi.</span></span>', 'VIETNAM EXPO – Capture opportunities, cooperate and grow together', 'The success of Vietnam Expo is not only a first-ever trade promotion event of Vietnam held annually for nearly three decades. It is also a well-known event because of the diversity of products, quality products - prestigious brand - creativity of Vietnam that introduces international friends.', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'vietnam-expo-capture-opportunities-cooperate-and-grow-together', '', '', '2019-06-22 23:59:15', '2019-06-22 16:59:15', '', 0, 'http://elevator_vnexpo.co/?p=207', 0, 'post', '', 0),
